  "response": "Yes, there are several Monster Hunter games available on PC. One of the most notable is \"Monster Hunter: World,\" which was released on PC in August 2018. It is a popular entry in the Monster Hunter series and has received several updates and expansions, including the \"Iceborne\" expansion. Another PC game in the series is \"Monster Hunter Rise,\" which was initially released for the Nintendo Switch and later became available on PC in January 2022. Both games offer players the chance to hunt a variety of monsters in expansive environments, either solo or with other players in cooperative multiplayer.",
